[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    119[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   3. **The conversation-state store and conversation-transcript archive are recipe-acute as the recruitment-prescreen-record store.** Patient-reported medical-history information captured during the prescreen is research data with specific consent posture; the architecture must specify the per-state and per-jurisdiction retention reconciliation, the patient-right-of-access workflow per HIPAA and per-state research-record access provisions, and the consent-revocation-and-data-purge workflow.
